title: GAS DELIVERY DRIVER TAKES UP 3 PARKING LOTS BECAUSE NO TIME TO WASTE
text:
GAS DELIVERY DRIVER TAKES UP 3 PARKING LOTS BECAUSE NO TIME TO WASTE   
Dear A.S.S. Editor Advertisement 
I know sometimes the gas delivery man is on a rush to complete many deliveries for gas. Many people are waiting to replace their empty gas tanks for new ones so they can cook. 
But still, why park like this? Cannot take a few more seconds to actually par properly ah? Other than parallel parking, angle parking, or perpendicular parking, can anybody else explain what kind of parking is this? That's three lots taken up! 
We make this guy famous! 
Mick 
A.S.S. Contributor Editor's Note:
